Class TestController

  • java.lang.Object
    • aucklanduni.ece.hc.controller.TestController

  • @Controller
@RequestMapping(value="/test")
public class TestController
extends java.lang.Object
    This controller is used to write data into database, so that you don't have to use command prompt to do that. It is created to help to debug, not part of the project.
